Live in London is a live concert recording of George Michael's finals
two concerts in London's Earls Court Exhibition Centre on 24 and 25
August 2008 as part of his 25 Live tour. This is the first live DVD
of George Michael's career. It was released on DVD (two discs release)
and Blu-ray (one BD with DTS-HD Master Audio and Dolby Digital
5.1 multichannel sound) formats on 7 December 2009 in the UK, Europe
and Australia, and on 8 December 2009 in the USA and Canada
